      • okHttpClientBuilder

        public okhttp3.OkHttpClient.Builder okHttpClientBuilder()
        Gets a reference to the OkHttpClient.Builder used to build the OkHttpRequestHandler's internal OkHttpClient. This allows you to fully customize the OkHttpClient that the resulting OkHttpRequestHandler will make HTTP requests through.
        Returns:
        OkHttpClient.Builder that will produce the OkHttpClient used by the OkHttpRequestHandler built by this.
